      <title>特朗普的大型经济学家已经迷上了华尔街</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/trump-s-big-picture-economist-already-has-wall-street-hooked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统想拆除全球经济秩序已不是什么秘密。他将尝试在自己的地方建造的东西还不清楚。华尔街转向斯蒂芬·米兰（Stephen Miran）寻求线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/trump-s-big-picture-economist-already-has-wall-street-hooked</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
